              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center">No</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-bold text-gray-900">CMS Power</td>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-rose-50 font-black text-[#E11D48]">Extremely powerful</td>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center">Basic</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-bold text-gray-900">AI Features</td>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center">Limited</td>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-rose-50 font-black text-[#E11D48]">AI templates</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-bold text-gray-900">Starting Price</td>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center">$23/month</td>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-rose-50 font-black text-[#E11D48]">$10/month</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-bold text-gray-900">Learning Curve</td>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center">Steep (4-6 weeks)</td>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-rose-50 font-black text-[#E11D48]">Gentle (10-30 min)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-bold text-gray-900">Target User</td>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-rose-50 font-black text-[#E11D48]">Professionals</td>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center">Beginners</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- MY EXPERIENCE CASE STUDY -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-rose-50 to-pink-50 border-[3px] border-[#E11D48] p-6 md:p-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">MY EXPERIENCE</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8 uppercase tracking-wider font-bold">Real testing, not theoretical comparison</p>

        <div class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-900 font-black mb-8">
          The 6-Week Learning Curve That Paid Off <span class="text-[#E11D48]">216x</span>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          <p class="text-lg">
            An agency owner needed a new client site. Custom design, complex interactions, CMS for case studies. She tried Dorik first‚Äî$15/month seemed appealing.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-white border-[2px] border-[#E11D48] p-6 my-6">
            <h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">THE DORIK ATTEMPT</h3>
            <p class="mb-2"><strong class="text-gray-900">Generated in:</strong> 90 seconds</p>
            <p class="mb-2"><strong class="text-gray-900">First impression:</strong> Template looked okay</p>
            <p class="mb-2"><strong class="text-gray-900">The problem:</strong> Couldn't customize layout the client wanted</p>
            <p class="mb-2"><strong class="text-gray-900">Missing features:</strong> No custom animations, limited interactions</p>
            <p class="mb-4"><strong class="text-gray-900">Constraint:</strong> Locked into template structure</p>
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-900"><strong class="text-[#E11D48]">Result:</strong> After 3 days fighting the system, she gave up</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border-[2px] border-[#E11D48] p-6 my-6">
            <h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">THE WEBFLOW JOURNEY</h3>
            <p class="mb-2"><strong class="text-gray-900">Week 1:</strong> Learning interface, box model, selector concept</p>
            <p class="mb-2"><strong class="text-gray-900">Week 2:</strong> Building custom layouts, reusable components</p>
            <p class="mb-2"><strong class="text-gray-900">Week 3-4:</strong> Complex interactions, scroll animations</p>
            <p class="mb-2"><strong class="text-gray-900">Week 5:</strong> CMS integration, case study templates</p>
            <p class="mb-4"><strong class="text-gray-900">Week 6:</strong> Polish, testing, launch</p>
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-900"><strong class="text-[#E11D48]">Total time:</strong> 6 weeks to launch</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-rose-100 border-l-[4px] border-[#E11D48] p-6 my-6">
            <h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">THE LAUNCH RESULT</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-800 mb-4">
              Stunning custom design that impressed everyone. Complex scroll animations that kept users engaged.
              CMS let client manage case studies independently.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-800 mb-4">
              <strong class="text-gray-900">Looked like a $50,000 site.</strong> Client was thrilled.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-800">
              Referred <strong class="text-[#E11D48]">3 new projects</strong> from the impressive portfolio.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-pink-100 border-l-[4px] border-pink-500 p-6 my-6">
            <h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">THE BRUTAL MATH</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm mb-4">
              <div>
                <p class="font-bold mb-2">Dorik (if it worked):</p>
                <p>‚Ä¢ Cost: $15/month = $180/year</p>
                <p>‚Ä¢ Template constraints = no referrals</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-bold mb-2">Webflow:</p>
                <p>‚Ä¢ Cost: $49/month = $588/year</p>
                <p>‚Ä¢ 3 referrals = $127,000 revenue</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="font-black text-gray-900">The 6-week investment paid for itself <span class="text-[#E11D48]">216x</span></p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border-[2px] border-[#E11D48] p-6 my-6">
            <h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">THE COUNTER-SCENARIO</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">
              A local plumber needed a simple site. Services, contact form, that's it.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-4">
              <strong class="text-gray-900">Tried Webflow first:</strong> Spent 2 weeks learning, realized it was overkill.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-4">
              <strong class="text-gray-900">Switched to Dorik:</strong> Generated in 90 seconds, added phone number, published in 10 minutes.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-rose-50 border-l-[4px] border-[#E11D48] p-4 my-4">
