              <p class="text-sm"><strong class="text-gray-900">Webflow:</strong> $588/year, $3,000/month revenue = <span class="text-gray-600">5.1x return</span></p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-red-100 border-l-[4px] border-red-500 p-6 my-6">
            <h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">THE LESSON</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-800">
              <strong class="text-gray-900">Designers, agencies, custom work:</strong> Webflow's power justifies the 6-week learning curve.
              The portfolio builds itself. Clients pay premium for custom work.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-800 mt-3">
              <strong class="text-gray-900">Local businesses, simple needs:</strong> Dorik delivers results faster and cheaper.
              Don't overpay for power you'll never use.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- UNEXPECTED FINDINGS -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
        <div class="w-2 h-12 bg-[#E11D48]"></div>
        UNEXPECTED FINDINGS
      </h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-gray-200 p-6 hover:border-[#E11D48] transition-colors">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-3">üìà</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Webflow Portfolio Builds Itself</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">After 6-week investment, the agency owner's first Webflow site generated 3 referrals worth $127,000. The portfolio became self-sustaining. Clients now come specifically for Webflow work.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-gray-200 p-6 hover:border-[#E11D48] transition-colors">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-3">‚è±Ô∏è</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Dorik Speed Is Underrated</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">10 minutes from zero to live site. For local businesses, this speed matters more than custom animations. The plumber got calls same-day. Speed = revenue when you're local.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-gray-200 p-6 hover:border-[#E11D48] transition-colors">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-3">üéì</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Learning Curve Is Barrier to Entry</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Webflow's 6-week learning curve prevents competition. Most quit before becoming productive. This scarcity keeps Webflow developer rates high ($75-150/hour). The barrier IS the moat.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-gray-200 p-6 hover:border-[#E11D48] transition-colors">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-3">üí∞</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Code Export Justifies Premium</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Webflow's code export means you're never locked in. Can migrate to custom hosting anytime. Dorik's platform lock-in means rebuild if you leave. That flexibility is worth $408/year to agencies.</p>
        </div>

